Directed By Denis Villeneuve.

Written By Denis Villeneuve. Jon Spaihts. Frank Herbert.

Cast Timothée Chalamet. Zendaya. Rebecca Ferguson.

Language English.

Producer Cale Boyter. Jessica Derhammer. Herbert W. Gains. Joshua Grode. John Harrison. Brian Herbert. Kim Herbert. Tanya Lapointe. Patrick McCormick. Byron Merritt. Mary Parent. Richard P. Rubinstein. Jon Spaihts. Thomas Tull. Denis Villeneuve.

Production Legendary Entertainment. Warner Bros. Entertainment. Villeneuve Films.
